latestPosts.caption:
Basic Hair-Care Guide: for Romantic Movie wala kind of Silky, Strong, Head-Turning Hair!
Weekly Routine
1. Shampoo: 2–3×/week — cleanse the scalp, don’t strip the strands. 
2.Conditioner: Every wash — apply mid-lengths to ends to lock in moisture. 
3.Hair Mask: 1×/week — deep treatment for repair & shine. 
4.Hair Oil: 1–2×/week or as needed — pre-wash protectant or post-wash shine booster. 
________________________________________
Listen to Your Hair
1.Dry hair? Increase conditioning & mask frequency.
2.Oily scalp? Focus shampoo on roots and cut heavy product usage.
3.Breakage? Add protein-rich masks and dial back heat styling. 
________________________________________
Tools & Techniques
1.Use a wide-tooth comb on damp hair—prevents breakage. 
 2.Pat with a microfiber towel—no rubbing, less frizz. 
Sleep on satin or silk pillowcases
3.Use silk/satin scrunchies or hair wraps
4.Use a scalp massager to stimulates blood flow and evenly spreads oils
